OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 23 MAY
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2005FBBC staff go on strike from
OL,7,Fmidnight on 23rd May 2005 for 24 hours.
OL,8,
OL,9,FThey are protesting at plans to cut
OL,10,F3,780 jobs and privatise parts of the
OL,11,FCorporation. The unions say the cuts
OL,12,Fare the most damaging in BBC history.
OL,13,FThe Corporation says it regrets the
OL,14,Fdecision to take industrial action.
OL,15,
OL,16,FThe strike posed the most serious
OL,17,Fthreat to the BBC's programming
OL,18,Fschedule across all TV and radio
OL,19,Fnetworks in over a decade.
